profile: At Floor Experts in Oromocto, we sell and install the very best in Luxury Vinyl Flooring, Click Lock Laminate Flooring, Hardwood Floors, Ceramic and Porcelain Tile, Carpet Tile and more. We are your Authorized Benjamin Moore Colour Studio and Hunter Douglas Window Treatment Specialists. We provide Hardwood refinishing, as well as Stair Systems. Commercial and Residential Projects welcome! Painters available. Call us today to talk about your project in the Oromocto and Fredericton area!
